name: fre.publicwebsites.nowcouriers
description: How to run the UI integration tests - local     Option 1: (via click and run)     $ npm install cypress --save-dev     $ ./node_modules/.bin/cypress open     Select the intended test and run     Option 2: (via CLI)     $ npm install cypress --save-dev     $ ./node_modules/.bin/cypress run     This runs all the tests from command line inteface
